HEADWORD: Lampic
<hw>Lam"pic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>lampique</ets>, fr. <ets>lampe</ets> lamp. See
<er>Lamp</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or produced
by, a lamp; -- formerly said of a supposed acid.</def>⟦br⟧
